For instance, instead of glitter, how about using some form of perminant ink, like banks use in their dye packs.  Neon orange, or pink.  And have 4 c02 powered directional nozzels (like your cameras) literally paint them and the entire room in seconds.  And the stink bomb probably smelled bad, but it could have been worse.
